text: Whether true style begins on or off the runway is the fashion industry's chicken or the egg. We won't reveal where our loyalties lie, but the industry's IRL interpretation of the biggest trends is an ongoing highlight of fashion week. ELLE.com's photographer Tyler Joe captured all the biggest moments from NYFW, including rain-slick looks, a shirtless Pete Davidson, and more.
authors: Justine Carreon Is The Market Editor At Elle.Com Covering Fashion
